<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing the Spirit Burn Passive Ability to immediately deal a tick of damage upon refreshing the duration of the ability.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Power reduced to 30, down from 35.</li><li>No longer gives Haste.</li><li>Now gives 200 Health.</li><li>No longer has the Expose Weakness passive ability.</li><li>Now has the Unique Passive - Soul Collector. Stacks gained on the Advanced item Might will carry over when upgrading into Decay.</li><li>The Unique Passive - Spirit Burn has been reworked.</li><li>Unique Passive - Spirit Burn: Dealing damage with abilities will deal 6% of the target's maximum Health over 3 seconds as magical damage. Damage against non-Shapers cannot exceed 320 total damage.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Updated the visual effect on this item.</li></ul>